---
// Newsletter Landing Page (design-only, no functionality)
const pageTitle = "Automation in Africa — Weekly Newsletter";
const pageDescription = "Sign up to receive weekly insights on automation across African markets. Join today and get a free 10‑page automation report.";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #ffffff;
        --panel: #f5f7fb;
        --muted: #5b667a;
        --text: #0b1020;
        --accent: #006a43;
        --accent-strong: #005a38;
        --ring: #006a4326;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji";
        background: radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 20% -10%, #e8f5ef 0%, #ffffff 70%), var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .container { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }

      /* Hero */
      .hero {
        padding: 72px 0 48px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .eyebrow { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px; }
      .title { font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.1; margin: 12px 0 16px; font-weight: 800; }
      .subtitle { color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 28px; }
      .lead-card {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #f7faff);
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 18px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px var(--ring);
      }
      .lead-badge { background: #e8f6ef; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 12px; }
      .lead-text { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); }

      .signup {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }
      .input {
        flex: 1;
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
        color: var(--text);
        padding: 14px 14px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        outline: none;
      }
      .button {
        background: var(--accent-strong);
        color: #ffffff;
        font-weight: 700;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .button:hover { background: var(--accent); }
      .hero-graphic {
        background: radial-gradient(400px 220px at 80% 20%, #daf2e6 0%, #e9f7ef 45%, #f7fbf9 80%);
        border: 1px solid #cdebd8;
        border-radius: 16px;
        height: 360px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .blob {
        position: absolute;
        width: 420px; height: 420px; border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #006a4322, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(10px);
        animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      @keyframes float { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(-6px);} 50% { transform: translateY(6px);} }
      .report {
        background: #ffffffcc;
        border: 1px solid #cdebd8;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }
      .report strong { color: var(--text); }

      /* Features */
      .section { padding: 36px 0 12px; }
      .section h2 { font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
      .section p.desc { margin: 0 0 24px; color: var(--muted); }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 18px;
      }
      .card {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #f9fbff);
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 16px;
      }
      .card h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 18px; }
      .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }

      /* CTA */
      .cta {
        margin: 32px 0 64px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e8f6ef, #f1fbf6);
        border: 1px solid #cdebd8;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 22px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: 16px;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .cta h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 22px; }
      .cta p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }

      /* Lists and utility */
      .bullets { margin: 0 0 18px; padding-left: 20px; color: var(--text); }
      .bullets li { margin: 8px 0; }
      .preview { background: #f5f7fb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; color: var(--muted); }
      .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
      .list-cross, .list-check { margin: 8px 0 0; padding-left: 20px; }
      .list-cross li { margin: 6px 0; list-style: "✗ "; }
      .list-check li { margin: 6px 0; list-style: "✓ "; }
      .report-details .bullets { margin-top: 8px; }

      /* Social proof */
      .social-proof .logos { height: 48px; display: grid; place-items: center; color: var(--muted); border: 1px dashed #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .testimonials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
      blockquote { margin: 0; padding: 14px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px; }
      blockquote footer { margin-top: 8px; color: var(--muted); }

      /* Form */
      .signup-full .form { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin-top: 8px; }
      .signup-full .row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
      .select { appearance: none; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; color: var(--text); padding: 14px; border-radius: 10px; }
      .button-lg { padding: 16px 22px; font-size: 14px; }
      .next-steps { margin: 12px 0 0; padding-left: 18px; color: var(--muted); }

      /* FAQ */
      .faq-items { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
      details { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 14px; }
      summary { cursor: pointer; }

      /* Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .cta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .testimonials { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        background: #f7fbf9;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }
      .footer-inner {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding-top: 18px;
        padding-bottom: 18px;
      }
      .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
      .logo {
        width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px;
        display: grid; place-items: center;
        background: #e8f6ef; color: var(--accent-strong);
        font-weight: 800;
      }
      .brand-name { margin: 0; font-size: 16px; }
      .brand-tag { margin: 2px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
      .social { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
      .icon { color: #334155; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-decoration: none; }
      .icon:hover { color: var(--accent-strong); border-color: #cdebd8; background: #f3faf6; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <!-- Hero with Lead Magnet -->
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Weekly Newsletter</div>
          <h1 class="title">Stop Losing to Competitors Who've Already Automated</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">Get weekly insights on practical automation strategies specifically designed for African manufacturers, distributors, and logistics providers. No theory. No fluff. Just actionable steps you can implement this week.</p>
          <div class="lead-card" role="note" aria-label="Lead magnet">
            <span class="lead-badge">Free Report</span>
            <p class="lead-text"><strong>The Automation Advantage:</strong> How African SMEs Are Cutting Costs by 20–35% Through Smart Technology — free 10‑page report.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="signup" aria-label="Newsletter signup">
            <input class="input" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" aria-label="Email" />
            <button class="button" type="button">Sign Up</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-graphic">
          <div class="blob"></div>
          <div class="report">
            <span>📘</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Automation Report 2025</strong>
              <div style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px;">10 pages • PDF</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What You'll Get -->
      <section class="section" id="features">
        <h2>What You’ll Get</h2>
        <p class="desc">Free weekly newsletter includes:</p>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li><strong>Practical automation wins</strong> you can implement with your current budget</li>
          <li><strong>Case studies from African businesses</strong> who've successfully automated (without breaking the bank)</li>
          <li><strong>Technology spotlights</strong> — tools that actually work for SMEs in Kenya and South Africa</li>
          <li><strong>Cost-benefit breakdowns</strong> so you know exactly what ROI to expect</li>
          <li><strong>Implementation roadmaps</strong> with realistic timelines for businesses your size</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="preview">
          <em>“How a Kenyan Coffee Exporter Cut Processing Time by 40% Using Simple Inventory Automation (Total Investment: Under $2,000)”</em>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Social Proof -->
      <section class="section social-proof" id="social-proof">
        <h2>Trusted by Operations Leaders At:</h2>
        <div class="logos">[Add logos/company names when available]</div>
        <div class="testimonials">
          <blockquote>
            <p>“Finally, automation advice that understands our market realities. No more wondering if Silicon Valley solutions will work in Johannesburg.”</p>
            <footer>— <strong>Sarah M.</strong>, Operations Manager, Cape Town</footer>
          </blockquote>
          <blockquote>
            <p>“The case studies are gold. Seeing how other African companies tackled similar challenges gave us the confidence to automate our warehouse.”</p>
            <footer>— <strong>James K.</strong>, Founder, Nairobi</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Problem / Solution -->
      <section class="section problem-solution" id="problem-solution">
        <div class="two-col">
          <div>
            <h2>The Challenge You’re Facing</h2>
            <ul class="list-cross">
              <li>Your competitors are cutting costs while your margins stay tight</li>
              <li>Manual processes are slowing down your growth</li>
              <li>You know automation could help, but don't know where to start</li>
              <li>Most automation advice assumes unlimited budgets and perfect infrastructure</li>
              <li>You're wasting time researching solutions that don't work in African markets</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2>What You Get Instead</h2>
            <ul class="list-check">
              <li><strong>Budget-conscious strategies</strong> designed for businesses earning R1M–R50M annually</li>
              <li><strong>Infrastructure-aware solutions</strong> that work with African connectivity and power realities</li>
              <li><strong>Proven case studies</strong> from businesses operating in similar conditions</li>
              <li><strong>Step-by-step implementation guides</strong> with realistic timelines</li>
              <li><strong>Cost calculations</strong> so you know exactly what to expect before investing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Free Report Details -->
      <section class="section report-details" id="free-report">
        <h2>Your Free Report: “The Automation Advantage”</h2>
        <p class="desc">10 pages of actionable insights including:</p>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li><strong>5 automation quick wins</strong> you can implement this month (under R10,000 each)</li>
          <li><strong>ROI calculator template</strong> to evaluate automation opportunities</li>
          <li><strong>Infrastructure checklist</strong> — what you need before automating</li>
          <li><strong>Vendor evaluation framework</strong> specifically for African market conditions</li>
          <li><strong>3 detailed case studies</strong> from Kenyan and South African businesses</li>
          <li><strong>Technology roadmap template</strong> for 6‑month automation planning</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="desc"><strong>Download immediately after signup</strong> — no waiting for email delivery.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- About -->
      <section class="section about" id="about">
        <h2>From SupplyCheck: Your Operational Technology Partners</h2>
        <p>We're not another software company trying to sell you expensive solutions. We're <strong>operational technology specialists</strong> who understand the unique challenges of running efficient businesses in African markets.</p>
        <p><strong>Our mission:</strong> Democratize access to AI and automation technology for businesses of all sizes.</p>
        <p><strong>Our experience:</strong> Working with 1–250 employee companies across manufacturing, distribution, and logistics in the UK‑Africa corridor.</p>
        <p><strong>Our approach:</strong> People first, technical credibility, above and beyond service.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Signup Form (design-only) -->
      <section class="section signup-full" id="signup">
        <h2>Ready to Stop Losing Ground to Automated Competitors?</h2>
        <p class="desc"><strong>Join 800+ African business leaders</strong> who get weekly automation insights delivered every Tuesday.</p>
        <form class="form" aria-label="Newsletter signup form (design-only)">
          <input class="input" type="email" placeholder="Email Address" aria-label="Email Address" />
          <div class="row">
            <select class="select" aria-label="Company Location">
              <option>Company Location</option>
              <option>South Africa</option>
              <option>Kenya</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
            <select class="select" aria-label="Industry">
              <option>Industry</option>
              <option>Manufacturing</option>
              <option>Distribution</option>
              <option>Logistics</option>
              <option>Retail</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <button type="button" class="button button-lg">GET MY FREE REPORT + WEEKLY INSIGHTS</button>
        </form>
        <ol class="next-steps">
          <li><strong>Instant access</strong> to your free automation report</li>
          <li><strong>Welcome email</strong> with 3 quick automation wins you can implement this week</li>
          <li><strong>Weekly newsletters</strong> every Tuesday (starting next week)</li>
          <li><strong>No spam, ever</strong> — unsubscribe anytime with one click</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <section class="section faq" id="faq">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-items">
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Is this newsletter only for big companies?</strong></summary>
            <p>No — we specifically focus on businesses with 1–250 employees. Most of our case studies and strategies are designed for companies with R1M–R50M annual revenue.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Will these strategies work with limited internet connectivity?</strong></summary>
            <p>Absolutely. All our recommendations consider African infrastructure realities. We focus on solutions that work reliably, not just on paper.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>How technical do I need to be?</strong></summary>
            <p>Not at all. We explain everything in plain language and focus on practical implementation, not technical theory.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Do you only cover expensive automation software?</strong></summary>
            <p>No — many of our featured solutions cost under R5,000 to implement. We always include budget-conscious alternatives.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>How long are the newsletters?</strong></summary>
            <p>3–5 minute reads. Packed with value, respectful of your time.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Can I unsubscribe anytime?</strong></summary>
            <p>Yes, one‑click unsubscribe in every email. No questions asked.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section class="cta" aria-labelledby="cta-title">
        <div>
          <h3 id="cta-title">Join 1,000+ readers accelerating automation</h3>
          <p>Subscribe now and get the free 10‑page Automation Report instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signup">
          <input class="input" type="email" placeholder="you@company.com" aria-label="Email" />
          <button class="button" type="button">Sign Up</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer" aria-labelledby="footer-title">
